# Test Rules

- Framework: pytest + pytest-asyncio (auto mode)
- Tests mirror source structure: `tests/unit/test_<module>.py`
- HTTP mocking: `respx`
- Time control: `time-machine`
- Mark slow tests with `@pytest.mark.integration`
- Every function in source needs at least one unit test
- Use `@pytest.fixture` for setup/teardown
- Async tests: `async def test_...()` with auto mode
- Test naming: `test_<function_name>_<scenario>`
